  "notes": [
    {
      "ref": "2:6",
      "title": "The faithless who refuse guidance",
      "text": "Here 'those who disbelieve' (<em>alladhīna kafarū</em>) does not mean every non-believer, but those set firmly upon denial — whose hearts are overtaken by hostility to the truth and who spare no effort fighting against God's religion. For such people, warning and admonition no longer make a difference.",
      "audio": {
        "v1": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note0_v1.mp3",
          "dur": 24.111
        },
        "v2": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note0_v2.mp3",
          "dur": 22.204
        },
        "celeste": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note0_celeste.mp3",
          "dur": 21.786
        }
      },
      "sources": [
        "al-Mīzān 1/55"
      ]
    },
    {
      "ref": "2:10",
      "title": "The heart — the essence of the human being",
      "text": "When the Qur'an speaks of the 'heart' (<em>qalb</em>), it means the very essence of the human being — their life and soul. Just as the body knows health, sickness, and death, so too does the heart: it can be sound, diseased, or dead. Hypocrisy is a sickness of the heart that, left untreated, only spreads.",
      "audio": {
        "v1": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note1_v1.mp3",
          "dur": 26.018
        },
        "v2": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note1_v2.mp3",
          "dur": 25.626
        },
        "celeste": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note1_celeste.mp3",
          "dur": 22.361
        }
      },
      "sources": [
        "al-Mīzān 2/228"
      ]
    },
    {
      "ref": "2:14",
      "title": "Shayṭān",
      "text": "The word 'shayṭān' (<em>shayṭān</em>) means one far removed from goodness — a being of evil. It is not only Iblīs: because he was driven so far from God's mercy, he became the very embodiment of evil, so that 'shayṭān' came to function almost as a proper name for him — though it can describe any rebellious, corrupting force.",
      "audio": {
        "v1": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note2_v1.mp3",
          "dur": 26.436
        },
        "v2": {
          "audio": "audio/day3_note2_v2.mp3",
          "dur": 27.925
        },
